title: MAHATRANSCO Notification 2026 - Apply Online for 29 Apprentice Posts
description: Maharashtra State Electricity Transmission Company (MAHATRANSCO) has declared the official notification for 2026. To fill up the vacancies for 29 Apprentice Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the 10th Pass and ITI can grab this chance and apply for the MAHATRANSCO Notification 2026 . Here, we included the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
